05開始升,到13跳崖式截停。人口老化同埋334改制似乎先係主因</blockquote><br />\n雙非生落黎既仔有貧血 本身可以好多雙非仔係大陸住 但係大大下發現有貧血所以咪落黎醫囉 所以咪呢個問題依家先爆發囉</blockquote><br />\n咁唔夠血呢個問題應該係196x年已經爆左出黎啦,個時大陸落黎既人口仲多個本土香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁一齊搵下果段期間有冇數據證明冇缺血先</blockquote><br />\n以前d大災難發生會告急捐血,但又真係好似未聽過話持續唔夠血到而家呢個地步，起碼90年代單程證高峰期都冇聽過，而家單程證人數比抵壘同90年代時都少,點解反而而家出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議你睇下呢篇文<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1043221\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1043221&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=0ba99106\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1043221&h=69ae7577\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1043221</a><br />\n<br />\n有詳細分析人口老化,遲婚及334對用血捐血既影響，有晒數據"},{"pid":"1ae626b66eecaf7e746a7e0462dec910e69e37b4","tid":232293,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T23:18:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就算唔講雙非衝閘， 人口老化問題本身都好大問題。 而家係老野嗰一代個個都生4~5個， 但係父母嗰一代就生1個，甚至唔生。 再過幾年呢班中年開始變老有病， 後生嗰班3個月捐一次都唔夠你消耗。 到時唯有強制捐血？</blockquote><br />\n雙非2012年停左<br />\n如果關雙非事2006年個時佢已經會見到d問題,雙非係由05開始升,到13跳崖式截停。人口老化同埋334改制似乎先係主因</blockquote><br />\n雙非生落黎既仔有貧血 本身可以好多雙非仔係大陸住 但係大大下發現有貧血所以咪落黎醫囉 所以咪呢個問題依家先爆發囉</blockquote><br />\n另外人口老化都係主要問題之一<br />\n但係334改制我就唔會認同 有數得計 <br />\n16歲可以捐血 而公開試果級唔捐<br />\n新制係中四中五捐 即係整整2級人既數目<br />\n舊制係中4 中6捐 但中6因為CE 西走左大半人 所以只有總計一級半既人捐到<br />\n另外大學亦有捐血活動 唔好理佢多唔多人捐 但係多左一級 就理應比舊制多左人捐血<br />\n即係334學制反而係會增加左捐血人數</blockquote><br />\n實際數據係改制後中學生捐血數字下降,呢個冇得厄"},{"pid":"094af0fc152b4de78bc23b542000685b116f2d75","tid":232293,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T23:22:29.000Z","msg":"睇數字就知334既影響<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20141229/photo/bkn-20141229215946479-1229_00822_001_13p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20141229%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20141229215946479-1229_00822_001_13p.jpg&h=b2c59e42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71add57fe343dd84f3eb6af1de39bcda6784c2dd","tid":232293,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T23:30:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b95108cc9061842d15ef48c1a702a5858aef30e","tid":232293,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T23:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7371878c5c82f486b8f828ff0154e3db3594a18","tid":232293,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T23:56:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af4784b1fe1e5ffdffe7b64be7cecf540924b062","tid":232293,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T00:19:41.000Z","msg":"留名今晚睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e1458deb9fd4d048deae6e7db920a559c125bd","tid":232293,"uid":5197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T00:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>私家賺嘅係服務 人手 equipment  唔係包血<br />\n去捐比啲對自己不利嘅人簡直荒謬 <br />\n香港人唔止血 根本連公立醫院十個有七個都係新香港人 有啲仲要係大陸醫院做過手術又換呢換路 大陸醫院醫閪左 就走返黎香港公立醫 要香港人埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:做醫院</blockquote><br />\n諗都諗到大把呢啲問題啦"},{"pid":"fe5075244992096d6166815986637d6d3f062744","tid":232293,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T00:31:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">血液誠可貴，膠喉價更高<br />\n</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0af915d5abe3792d27775236a948fbbbadb5e28","tid":232293,"uid":83015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T00:52:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6y5a07V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6y5a07V.jpg&h=97f11038&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/034033_67cb435b02d50e31de586c31bc06d1eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F034033_67cb435b02d50e31de586c31bc06d1eb.jpg&h=33f1db64&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/034041_b27dbea680f246f768cbc03793657e98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F034041_b27dbea680f246f768cbc03793657e98.jpg&h=12be2d88&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅十字會 都是 社會一份子， 唔夠血，問題不在 香港人都應該反映下。不是容忍政府不當"},{"pid":"2a7eeb40ddb9592d38efb784a6105d48dcb73554","tid":232293,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:06:24.000Z","msg":"其實我自己睇返d資料334時間上係吻合因素"},{"pid":"b17e9b1181ef569a11f42a32991356650e549388","tid":232293,"uid":81345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:12:05.000Z","msg":"吓，唔捐血都唔得？<br />\n唔見你捐錢比我？<br />\n成日道德綁架"},{"pid":"c43882755872ad47c50235e62a0d3370867efb6b","tid":232293,"uid":113312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/90re1bpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F90re1bpg&h=9d679f19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實唔關334事，出生率下降，高中生數目自然減少"},{"pid":"e1c4184bdfbb21b5659eb7495847683c29a0be2b","tid":232293,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:21:59.000Z","msg":"從來就民無信不立, 政府沒有信用, 不被信任, 那所有東西都會隨之崩潰. 當香港有一個不斷要人不效忠自己的城市, 叫人移民離開自己城市的政府, 卻同時要說服別人捐血給自己的城市. 這不是自相矛盾嗎. 捐血這種義務是為了維持令這地方是個適合居住的好地方, 大家才願意做的, 如果連政府都不在意這地方是否適合這裡的人居住, 說不滿的人就滾, 被說服了真的想離開的人又為何要對這裡貢獻甚麼?<br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap"},{"pid":"d1886cd6d9a8e410f6a75e4a85cc6bea2f4a9b98","tid":232293,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:25:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好有PR狗打手放鱔Feel囉！！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50d02866bebca1852f6e5791456382df995fcbf","tid":232293,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:28:06.000Z","msg":"捐血事件搞到今日咁。 係社會撕裂既結果嚟既啫。 咩成本要三千， 學生少左。 依啲解釋都唔係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  後生一代對社會失望失信先係重點"},{"pid":"17390dbe596337860be97d941b2411b6b9b2f0ec","tid":232293,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:29:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"185bf0c3b1f5a4dcf16fb8da14122b6bdc88c4c9","tid":232293,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:30:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4be205c2f783402d8f131bc832e353547ab44aa2","tid":232293,"uid":4360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:33:09.000Z","msg":"學生少咗咁又點<br />\n點解一定要向最後生仲發育期緊嘅學生落手<br />\n而家個logic就好似最老個班一定要靠最後生個班俾血佢，唔俾就係大罪人<br />\n明明社會上仲有好多其他人 eg公務員 紀律部隊 大企業<br />\n咪撚再賴落班後生嘅到"},{"pid":"8d3a3abae763c1489d1cedbb586ce3cb16ba1d6f","tid":232293,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇數字就知334既影響<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20141229/photo/bkn-20141229215946479-1229_00822_001_13p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20141229%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20141229215946479-1229_00822_001_13p.jpg&h=b2c59e42&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢青 證明DSE 廢過AL</blockquote><br />\n其實DSE學生同AL總數差唔多,少左人捐係咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有睇返總捐血量無少過,即係demand多左係真的<br />\n<br />\ndemand多左雙非,新移民同人口老化三樣加埋應該先係主因"},{"pid":"ecff6df9d10acf44bfa012c665dba9b61537501c","tid":232293,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:38:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學生少咗咁又點<br />\n點解一定要向最後生仲發育期緊嘅學生落手<br />\n而家個logic就好似最老個班一定要靠最後生個班俾血佢，唔俾就係大罪人<br />\n明明社會上仲有好多其他人 eg公務員 紀律部隊 大企業<br />\n咪撚再賴落班後生嘅到</blockquote><br />\n因為65歲以上唔俾捐,但呢班人用左差唔多3成血"},{"pid":"0791f49908e5d50357b2c9dcd7f6ae849e6619e9","tid":232293,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:38:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[img]://<a href=\"http://na.cx/i/6y5a07V.jpg[/img][img]https:img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/034033_67cb435b02d50e31de586c31bc06d1eb.jpg[/img][img]https:/img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/034041_b27dbea680f246f768cbc03793657e98.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6y5a07V.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D%5Bimg%5Dhttps%3Aimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F034033_67cb435b02d50e31de586c31bc06d1eb.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D%5Bimg%5Dhttps%3A%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F034041_b27dbea680f246f768cbc03793657e98.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=933c904f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">na.cx/i/6y5a07V.jpg[/img][img]https:img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/034033_67cb435b02d50e31de586c31bc06d1eb.jpg[/img][img]https:/img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/034041_b27dbea680f246f768cbc03793657e98.jpg[/img]</a></blockquote><br />\n香港人係唔見棺材唔流眼淚，你一日唔做到最絕，佢一日當你係傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但程證2006年佢做個幾年數字絕對多過近呢幾年，賴落新移民到一睇數據就知講唔通<br />\n<br />\n[imgttp://<a href=\"http://s9.rr.itc.cn/r/wapChange/20173_2_12/a70p6r63502886340405.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs9.rr.itc.cn%2Fr%2FwapChange%2F20173_2_12%2Fa70p6r63502886340405.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=db7bce76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">s9.rr.itc.cn/r/wapChange/20173_2_12/a70p6r63502886340405.jpg[/img]</a></blockquote><br />\n如果係滾雪球式<br />\n咁要延後幾年先黎比較先叫準"},{"pid":"2ff824948fa3d5cd86eefc5c60ced6b6b2c8918c","tid":232293,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:40:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>[img]://<a href=\"http://na.cx/i/6y5a07V.jpg[/img][img]https:img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/034033_67cb435b02d50e31de586c31bc06d1eb.jpg[/img][img]https:/img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/034041_b27dbea680f246f768cbc03793657e98.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6y5a07V.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D%5Bimg%5Dhttps%3Aimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F034033_67cb435b02d50e31de586c31bc06d1eb.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D%5Bimg%5Dhttps%3A%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F07%2F034041_b27dbea680f246f768cbc03793657e98.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=933c904f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">na.cx/i/6y5a07V.jpg[/img][img]https:img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/034033_67cb435b02d50e31de586c31bc06d1eb.jpg[/img][img]https:/img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/07/034041_b27dbea680f246f768cbc03793657e98.jpg[/img]</a></blockquote><br />\n香港人係唔見棺材唔流眼淚，你一日唔做到最絕，佢一日當你係傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但程證2006年佢做個幾年數字絕對多過近呢幾年，賴落新移民到一睇數據就知講唔通<br />\n<br />\n[imgttp://<a href=\"http://s9.rr.itc.cn/r/wapChange/20173_2_12/a70p6r63502886340405.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs9.rr.itc.cn%2Fr%2FwapChange%2F20173_2_12%2Fa70p6r63502886340405.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=db7bce76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">s9.rr.itc.cn/r/wapChange/20173_2_12/a70p6r63502886340405.jpg[/img]</a></blockquote><br />\n如果係滾雪球式<br />\n咁要延後幾年先黎比較先叫準</blockquote><br />\n老老豆豆做過lab佢睇到HKID就知係咪新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3649edd24f5c20287dcc84411a6ec54092fa249","tid":232293,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:43:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>就算唔講雙非衝閘， 人口老化問題本身都好大問題。 而家係老野嗰一代個個都生4~5個， 但係父母嗰一代就生1個，甚至唔生。 再過幾年呢班中年開始變老有病， 後生嗰班3個月捐一次都唔夠你消耗。 到時唯有強制捐血？</blockquote><br />\n雙非2012年停左<br />\n如果關雙非事2006年個時佢已經會見到d問題,雙非係由05開始升,到13跳崖式截停。人口老化同埋334改制似乎先係主因</blockquote><br />\n雙非生落黎既仔有貧血 本身可以好多雙非仔係大陸住 但係大大下發現有貧血所以咪落黎醫囉 所以咪呢個問題依家先爆發囉</blockquote><br />\n咁唔夠血呢個問題應該係196x年已經爆左出黎啦,個時大陸落黎既人口仲多個本土香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但數字同現實就顯示另一方面<br />\n<br />\n會唔會係新黎呢班蝗入面，有懚性病既人比以前多左好多？"},{"pid":"2dcb99c8c55a53a40f7d0748e4d424dc2dbd4689","tid":232293,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:47:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d8e50b6d68fc372bf9d4d91429c868400d74f93","tid":232293,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:47:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇數字就知334既影響<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20141229/photo/bkn-20141229215946479-1229_00822_001_13p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20141229%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20141229215946479-1229_00822_001_13p.jpg&h=b2c59e42&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果13年後數字仲係下跌，咁即係唔關334<br />\n係中學生人數少左既問題"},{"pid":"2b4d821fcc9d79fce45d6a74860f6ec6f48502fc","tid":232293,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:50:41.000Z","msg":"一句講晒<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.redcross.org.hk/files/images/logo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redcross.org.hk%2Ffiles%2Fimages%2Flogo.gif&h=3e718b25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f79f983fb8b5c1c2d17174c88b1162af5b4e2bb","tid":232293,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T01:54:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}